        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 0,
        "start": 55,
        "end": 59
      },
      "kind": "semantic",
      "text": "脫下貂皮大衣，覆蓋在書生身上。貂︰指貂皮製的大衣",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "149-14",
