        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 1,
        "start": 36,
        "end": 38
      },
      "kind": "semantic",
      "text": "古代的酷刑，用燒紅鐵器灼燙受刑者的身體。炮︰",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "149-26",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 1,
        "start": 39,
        "end": 43
      },
      "kind": "semantic",
      "text": "很快就會死亡。旦夕︰早晨和晚上，指很短的時間。且︰將",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "149-27",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 1,
        "start": 63,
        "end": 70
      },
      "kind": "pronunciation",
      "lang": "yue",
      "text": "據；geoi3",
      "source": "cham"
    },
